title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - Animated Promo Present
description:
You can use this template with all kind of product, service, company promos and presentations. There are 16 expandable placeholders for your content, photo, video and logo. There are ready to use 3 versions for 16/13/10 placeholders. Just add your content drag and drop it and press render.

Main features are:

After Effects CS5 and above compatible.
This is an AE project based on pre-rendered sequences.
Each placeholder comes with a unique pre-rendered loop animation sequence.
You can loop the animations as many placeholders as you like.
